name: Fuyara and Bluebird of Happiness
description: 幸せを運ぶ青い鳥がフヤラと歌を歌う sign of prosperity, good health and confidence  symbol of happy love and laughter spirit of rising sun   “In Japan, up on the mountain,  above the temple of Bishamonten,  the fuyara flute and bluebird  are singing a beautiful song  together  duet for eternal happiness.”
